# 环境变量模板 / Runtime env template

## 语言切换 / Language

- 中文（默认）: [本页](feishu-webhook.env.example)
- English: [Runtime env template](../docs/en/runtime-config.md)

This file is a template for the runtime env file mounted as `FEISHU_ENV_FILE`.

## 运行时配置 / Runtime config

# Required / 必填
WEBHOOK_SHARED_TOKEN=replace_me_with_long_random_secret
FEISHU_APP_ID=cli_xxx
FEISHU_APP_SECRET=replace_me

# Optional with defaults / 可选（有默认值）
FEISHU_BASE_URL=https://open.feishu.cn
HOST=0.0.0.0
PORT=2398
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
HTTP_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=10
TOKEN_REFRESH_SKEW_SECONDS=300

# Dynamic mode / 动态模式
FEISHU_TARGETS_FILE=/runtime/feishu-targets.toml
FEISHU_TARGET_RELOAD_INTERVAL_SECONDS=10
CONFIG_RELOAD_TOKEN=replace_me_with_admin_reload_token

# Legacy compatibility mode only / 仅旧版兼容模式使用
# FEISHU_APP_TOKEN=bascn_xxx
# FEISHU_TABLE_ID=tblxxx
# FEISHU_RECORD_ID=recxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# FEISHU_ORIGINAL_FIELD_NAME=原始信息
